                <h1>Mastering Background Apps: Boost Performance & Save Battery</h1>
                <p>Background apps are software programs that run behind the scenes on your device, helping to perform tasks without direct user interaction. They optimize system performance, manage notifications, or sync data in real-time. However, excessive background activity can drain battery life and slow down the device, so it's important to manage them effectively.</p>
